name: SecondBTC
description: Secondbtc has unveiled an innovative approach to #cryptocurrency exchanges by releasing its official token on pump.fun and empowering the community. Launching a token on the pump.fun memecoin platform sets this project apart, as no cryptocurrency exchange has launched their exchange token on a platform like pump.fun that allows users to purchase any quantity of supply. Secondbtc allocated 97% of its total supply to the public.
